To cite the use of Eilmer in publications, please use:

Gollan, R.J. and Jacobs, P.A. (2013)
About the formulation, verification and validation of
the hypersonic sonic flow solver Eilmer.
International Journal for Numerical Methods in Fluids, Vol. 73, pp. 19-57

As a BibTeX entry:

@Article{gollan_jacobs_2013,
  author = {Gollan, R. J. and Jacobs, P. A.},
  title = {About the formulation, verification and validation of the hypersonic flow solver Eilmer},
  journal = {International Journal for Numerical Methods in Fluids},
  year = {2013},
  volume = {73},
  pages = {19--57}
}

